religion and the practice of faith in the Christian Church merely apologetic in nature, or did they have a reasonable – in other words – scientific, philosophical basis? These were central questions at a symposium which was organized by the Schleiermacher Research Center of the Berlin Brandenburg Academy of Sciences in May 2009. The papers collected in this volume deal with these questions from the perspective of various disciplines.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aDeutscher Idealismus. 4aKirchengeschichte. 4aReligion. 4aSchleiermacher. 4aevangelische Theologie. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / General.2bisacsh  aChurch History.  aGerman Idealism.  aProtestant Theology.  aReligion.  aSchleiermacher.1 aArndt, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aArndt, Andreas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGerber, Simon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrosshans, Hans-Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOhst, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aScheliha, Arnulf von, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSelge, Kurt-Victor, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSelge, Kurt-Victor, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aVosskamp, Wilhelm, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2011z9783110261189oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET THEOLOGIE/RELIGIONSWISS./JUDAISTIK  2011z9783110261271o